imdb.plot outline: Guillermo Graziani (Julio Chávez) is a lawyer, leader by nature, the owner of a law firm, and the best in his field, he is married with Ana but has a double life, because he is gay, his wife knows all about it, and blackmails him with this fact. Guillermo was unable to work for a time thanks to his stepbrother (who seeks revenge and won't stop until he destroy Guillermo life), after a time he opens again his law firm. He has a son product of an occasional relationship Fabian (Chino Darín) Guillermo wants to conceal his homosexuality for his family sake. He has a crush, on Pedro but respect him very much, this makes him think he must be really in love with Pedro, since he always treat the other guys just like toys he can drop anytime. Ana (Ingrid Pelicori) Wife of Guillermo, finds refuge in alcohol to endure her life since she is not ready to lose the status of a wife and a wealthy life. Pedro Beggio (Benjaín Vicuña)is a very sensitive person that was working for his fiancé father, and got tired of it. He quit and ask Guillermo for a job. Pedro is confused about the marriage with Camila, and has many doubts about his feelings, his life start to change when he realizes he think about Guillermo all the time. Camila Moravia (Julieta Cardinali) is Pedro fiancé the first and only woman he had in his life, she dreams to be the perfect couple but she is too possessive about love. Alberto Marini (Facundo Arana) a former prisoner that works in the law firm, he is in charge of the rude duties and deals with them. He is loyal to Guillermo. Marcos Labrapoulos (Alfredo Casero) lawyer of the firm. He is married but he cheats on his wife with every girl that attracts him. Gabriela Soria (Griselda Sciciliani) lawyer of the firm. She has a long term boyfriend but starts to sense attraction for Alberto.
